### Academic Research Inspirations

This software implements concepts from:
- HippoRAG (Bernal et al., NeurIPS 2024)
- Hippocampal Indexing Theory (Teyler & Rudy, 2007)
- Word2Vec (Mikolov et al., 2013)
- Reciprocal Rank Fusion (Cormack et al., SIGIR 2009)
- Voyager (Wang et al., 2023)

See README.md Research & Credits section for complete citations.
